  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Install, service, maintain and repair air-conditioning and ventilation systems</p></li><li><p>Conduct routine inspections and preventive maintenance of air-conditioning units</p></li><li><p>Diagnose system faults and carry out troubleshooting and corrective repairs</p></li><li><p>Perform cleaning, chemical washing and replacement of faulty components</p></li><li><p>Ensure all works comply with safety regulations and company procedures</p></li><li><p>Prepare service reports and maintenance records after each job</p></li><li><p>Respond to breakdowns and service calls in a timely manner</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with supervisors and customers to ensure work completion and quality standards</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper use and care of tools, equipment and materials</p></li></ul>",
